Requirements
------------

You will need the following prerequisites in order to use pytest-metadata:

- Python 2.7, 3.6, PyPy, or PyPy3
- pytest 2.9.0 or newer

Installation
------------

To install pytest-metadata:

.. code-block:: bash

  $ pip install pytest-metadata

